1
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:35,020
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,830 --> 00:01:39,210
[2022]

3
00:01:37,870 --> 00:01:39,400
Okay, I have no problem with that.

4
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,120
Just pay more attention

5
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:40,840
to this.

6
00:01:41,039 --> 00:01:42,300
And just do it this way.

7
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,280
Mr. Wang.

8
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:49,280
What is it?

9
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,039
Well...

10
00:01:50,350 --> 00:01:53,479
It's about the collaboration
with Xing Min Technology.

11
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:56,580
We can't do it this way, right?

12
00:01:57,759 --> 00:01:58,890
Can't do it this way?

13
00:01:59,000 --> 00:01:59,400
Yes.

14
00:01:59,509 --> 00:02:00,840
Then how should we do it?

15
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,080
I entrusted this

16
00:02:02,110 --> 00:02:02,910
to you before.

17
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:05,100
Did you handle it well?

18
00:02:09,100 --> 00:02:10,240
Okay, look, Xia Xiaolan.

19
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,640
Let me ask you a question.

20
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,800
How long's it been since you graduated?

21
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:17,000
How long have you been in this industry?

22
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:17,630
Do you plan

23
00:02:17,630 --> 00:02:18,420
to just keep your head down

24
00:02:18,420 --> 00:02:19,480
and work like this?

25
00:02:19,760 --> 00:02:21,190
Can you please think about

26
00:02:21,190 --> 00:02:22,210
what kind of person

27
00:02:22,210 --> 00:02:22,940
you want to be

28
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,690
and what kind of life you want to live?

29
00:02:24,690 --> 00:02:25,470
Can you even try to be

30
00:02:25,470 --> 00:02:26,600
a bit clear-headed?

31
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,610
What are you looking at?

32
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,650
Are you done with your work?

33
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:35,470
Fine.

34
00:02:35,470 --> 00:02:37,310
Everyone stays to work overtime tonight.

35
00:02:37,310 --> 00:02:39,040
It's all thanks to Xia Xiaolan.

36
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:47,820
[Episode 33: What kind of life
do you want?]

37
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:54,840
You haven't

38
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:57,100
hit me up in a while, Second Young Master.

39
00:03:01,190 --> 00:03:02,240
Xia Xiaolan and Du Zhaohui

40
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,520
won the competition.

41
00:03:03,910 --> 00:03:05,110
Second Young Master,

42
00:03:05,750 --> 00:03:08,350
are you really going to sit back
and do nothing?

43
00:03:09,290 --> 00:03:10,910
Then, Ms. Vivi, please tell me

44
00:03:10,910 --> 00:03:11,840
what I should do.

45
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:16,140
I neither have Zhaohui's capability

46
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:17,710
to win Daddy's favor,

47
00:03:19,470 --> 00:03:21,930
nor can I get pregnant
to secure my position.

48
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:24,430
What should I do?

49
00:03:26,750 --> 00:03:28,600
Why mock yourself, Second Young Master?

50
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:29,160
It's just

51
00:03:29,190 --> 00:03:30,520
5% of the shares.

52
00:03:31,410 --> 00:03:32,740
The game isn't over yet.

53
00:03:33,490 --> 00:03:34,400
It's still

54
00:03:35,110 --> 00:03:35,970
anyone's game.

55
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:45,800
Sometimes I really envy

56
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,260
your innocence, Ms. Vivi.

57
00:03:48,430 --> 00:03:49,590
Do you think Daddy actually cares

58
00:03:49,590 --> 00:03:50,990
about this competition?

59
00:03:51,110 --> 00:03:52,970
He cares about no one but Zhaohui.

60
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:56,370
Even I, his grown son,

61
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,660
don't mean much to him.

62
00:03:59,870 --> 00:04:01,400
As for the one in your belly,

63
00:04:02,710 --> 00:04:03,970
how much could he care?

64
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:06,960
Even though Daddy

65
00:04:07,940 --> 00:04:09,050
won't lay a hand

66
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:10,030
on his own son,

67
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:12,910
if he finds out that you're

68
00:04:12,910 --> 00:04:14,710
playing tricks behind his back,

69
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:17,779
would he keep the child
and get rid of the mother?

70
00:04:36,390 --> 00:04:37,000
No.

71
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:41,190
He saw that the Master gave me status

72
00:04:41,950 --> 00:04:43,880
and privileges of doing business,

73
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:46,159
so he's afraid that the child in my belly

74
00:04:46,159 --> 00:04:47,420
will be a threat to him.

75
00:04:48,310 --> 00:04:48,680
Yes.

76
00:04:49,830 --> 00:04:50,690
That must be it.

77
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:56,409
Everyone wants to see me
make a fool of myself.

78
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,950
But I will still steal all the spotlight.

79
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:08,070
Master.

80
00:05:09,330 --> 00:05:11,750
The photo session took too long.

81
00:05:11,770 --> 00:05:13,400
My legs are sore.

82
00:05:13,830 --> 00:05:14,830
Serves you right.

83
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,560
No one forced you to do it.

84
00:05:16,740 --> 00:05:18,240
You said you wanted to learn

85
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,120
to do business.

86
00:05:20,450 --> 00:05:21,450
Didn't I do it

87
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,680
to share your burden?

88
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:23,920
Besides,

89
00:05:24,270 --> 00:05:25,510
when our baby is born,

90
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:26,720
he will say,

91
00:05:26,980 --> 00:05:28,160
"Mommy is pretty

92
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:29,720
but incapable of doing anything else."

93
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,050
Who will lose face then?

94
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:34,720
Very well.

95
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:36,040
Since you like attending

96
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,270
these events so much,

97
00:05:37,870 --> 00:05:38,470
there just

98
00:05:38,870 --> 00:05:40,750
happens to be a banquet
at the Jockey Club.

99
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:41,560
I don't want to go.

100
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:42,560
You go in my place.

101
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:45,240
It won't be too tiring, I think.

102
00:05:45,770 --> 00:05:46,650
I knew you

103
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:48,140
treat me the best, Master.

104
00:05:54,170 --> 00:05:57,520
[Shengcheng Oriental Green Golf Club
Tee-off Ceremony]

105
00:05:54,270 --> 00:05:54,930
Am I pretty?

106
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:58,060
The one beside me is prettier.

107
00:06:00,390 --> 00:06:02,120
Tell me whatever you want to eat.

108
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,850
I'll make it and bring it to you.

109
00:06:04,430 --> 00:06:04,920
Okay.

110
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:07,650
But I think the soup you make is

111
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:08,290
so delicious.

112
00:06:08,290 --> 00:06:09,560
I've improved, right?

113
00:06:09,630 --> 00:06:10,270
Yes.

114
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:12,510
Mom?

115
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:14,330
Welcome back, Xiaolan.

116
00:06:14,430 --> 00:06:15,600
I made some buns

117
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,410
and brought them for Granny Yu.

118
00:06:19,190 --> 00:06:19,800
Granny Yu.

119
00:06:20,590 --> 00:06:22,390
I'm going to Kong Island tomorrow.

120
00:06:22,390 --> 00:06:24,050
Do you want me to send anything

121
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,310
or any messages?

122
00:06:26,630 --> 00:06:28,270
I have nothing to say.

123
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:31,020
Those who want to come back

124
00:06:31,310 --> 00:06:32,840
will come back on their own.

125
00:06:35,390 --> 00:06:36,560
I won't see you out.

126
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:39,100
Go ahead and chat with your daughter.

127
00:06:39,159 --> 00:06:39,530
Okay.

128
00:06:40,270 --> 00:06:41,610
Rest early then.

129
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:42,120
Okay.

130
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:09,940
Granny Yu.

131
00:08:12,900 --> 00:08:13,430
Morning.

132
00:08:19,790 --> 00:08:21,030
Give this to him.

133
00:08:24,890 --> 00:08:27,420
There's nothing else I want to say.

134
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:30,190
Okay.

135
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:32,570
I'm leaving now.

136
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:32,929
Okay.

137
00:08:35,789 --> 00:08:36,360
Xiaolan.

138
00:08:38,890 --> 00:08:40,010
Take care of yourself

139
00:08:40,010 --> 00:08:41,539
when you reach Kong Island.

140
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:45,460
I'm off.

141
00:08:46,030 --> 00:08:46,480
Yes.

142
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:06,570
[Kong Island]

143
00:09:31,920 --> 00:09:33,940
[The 6th International Youth
Architectural Design Festival]

144
00:09:37,890 --> 00:09:38,600
She's left?

145
00:09:39,890 --> 00:09:40,840
Ms. Xia came to Kong Island

146
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:41,640
for business.

147
00:09:42,050 --> 00:09:43,380
She couldn't stay long.

148
00:09:43,540 --> 00:09:45,360
She asked me to give this to you.

149
00:09:54,110 --> 00:09:55,910
Did she leave any other message?

150
00:09:56,870 --> 00:09:57,320
No.

151
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,640
You may leave.

152
00:10:12,030 --> 00:10:12,830
In the future,

153
00:10:13,300 --> 00:10:14,360
who else will remember

154
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:17,020
that Xu Zhongyi was born
in the Year of the Tiger?

155
00:10:21,060 --> 00:10:23,260
I've come to realize

156
00:10:23,370 --> 00:10:24,840
that in the past seven years,

157
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:27,200
we've had many oriental faces

158
00:10:27,550 --> 00:10:31,080
and elements in this competition.

159
00:10:31,510 --> 00:10:35,120
And this, for the architectural sector, is

160
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:37,870
very, very good.

161
00:10:42,390 --> 00:10:43,030
Lady!

162
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:48,170
Now you want me to strike
the opening gong?

163
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:50,840
Lady,

164
00:10:51,150 --> 00:10:52,360
if you wish to leave,

165
00:10:52,430 --> 00:10:53,440
please take this passage

166
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:55,300
to the parking lot to get your car.

167
00:10:55,630 --> 00:10:57,790
Who cares about striking that crappy gong?

168
00:10:57,790 --> 00:10:58,870
Disrespecting me

169
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:01,370
means disrespecting Chairman Du.

170
00:11:02,830 --> 00:11:04,090
Where is the restroom?

171
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:12,920
We hope that this will bring closer
the East and the West

172
00:11:13,250 --> 00:11:14,650
together in the future.

173
00:11:14,910 --> 00:11:16,090
Thank you, Professor McCarthy,

174
00:11:16,090 --> 00:11:17,620
for your wonderful speech.

175
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:22,750
A dancing girl is just a dancing girl.

176
00:11:22,750 --> 00:11:24,410
She'll never be presentable.

177
00:11:24,590 --> 00:11:25,920
This is the Jockey Club.

178
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:28,390
Look at how much skin she's showing.

179
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:30,740
Mr. Du didn't teach her any manners.

180
00:11:30,740 --> 00:11:33,500
She's just embarrassing
the Du family out there.

181
00:11:34,590 --> 00:11:37,190
Mr. Du is known for his wild ways.

182
00:11:37,450 --> 00:11:40,300
He wouldn't actually
fall for a dancing girl.

183
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:44,920
Of course he wouldn't bother
teaching her etiquette.

184
00:11:45,550 --> 00:11:47,410
It's only because she's

185
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:49,010
pregnant.

186
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:51,200
If she's pregnant, she should stay home

187
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,440
and rest for the baby.

188
00:11:52,760 --> 00:11:54,030
Did you see the look on her face

189
00:11:54,030 --> 00:11:55,150
when the gong was struck?

190
00:11:55,150 --> 00:11:57,670
She actually thought
she could go on stage and strike it.

191
00:11:57,670 --> 00:11:58,750
What a joke.

192
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:00,910
If it weren't for Mr. Du's fame,

193
00:12:01,030 --> 00:12:02,670
she wouldn't even have a seat.

194
00:12:02,670 --> 00:12:03,700
Honestly.

195
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,150
Mrs. Chen, Mrs. Li,

196
00:12:12,150 --> 00:12:13,150
don't rush off.

197
00:12:14,270 --> 00:12:16,530
Weren't you enjoying chatting just now?

198
00:12:16,930 --> 00:12:17,880
I just wondered

199
00:12:17,910 --> 00:12:19,310
how capable you two were.

200
00:12:19,950 --> 00:12:22,210
But aren't you just relying
on your husbands' reputation

201
00:12:22,210 --> 00:12:22,910
to be in the same venue

202
00:12:22,910 --> 00:12:24,040
with a dancing girl?

203
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:26,070
Besides,

204
00:12:26,910 --> 00:12:28,410
what's wrong with dancing girls?

205
00:12:28,410 --> 00:12:29,450
Your husbands

206
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:30,440
sent you away,

207
00:12:31,040 --> 00:12:31,840
but right now,

208
00:12:32,170 --> 00:12:33,410
they could be

209
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:35,040
in some dancing girls' beds.

210
00:12:35,550 --> 00:12:37,320
With such stiff bones,

211
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,260
can you even dance?

212
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,600
The second prize goes

213
00:12:43,660 --> 00:12:44,780
to Xinghe Theater,

214
00:12:45,790 --> 00:12:46,600
designed

215
00:12:46,630 --> 00:12:48,030
by Xia Xiaolan

216
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:49,670
from Qi Hang Design Studio.

217
00:12:49,670 --> 00:12:52,200
Let's give a round of applause
to welcome her.

218
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:05,720
Congratulations. Well-done.

219
00:13:06,070 --> 00:13:07,070
See you next year.

220
00:13:07,100 --> 00:13:07,700
Thank you.

221
00:13:26,310 --> 00:13:27,570
Let me help you wash it.

222
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:29,210
Come on.

223
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:39,870
Good.

224
00:13:45,070 --> 00:13:45,980
Xia Xiaolan, you...

225
00:13:45,980 --> 00:13:47,380
You splashed water on me.

226
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:48,910
Let me do it.

227
00:13:55,270 --> 00:13:56,270
Comrade Xiaolan.

228
00:13:56,610 --> 00:13:57,430
Let's take a break.

229
00:13:57,430 --> 00:13:58,960
I'll pour you a cup of water.

230
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:05,930
Here you are.

231
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:07,600
Thank you.

232
00:14:17,510 --> 00:14:18,170
Be careful.

233
00:14:20,550 --> 00:14:21,610
The sun is blazing.

234
00:14:22,150 --> 00:14:23,280
It's scorching hot.

235
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:24,730
Isn't this Xiaolan?

236
00:14:25,150 --> 00:14:26,200
You wrote this.

237
00:14:26,260 --> 00:14:26,960
What is this?

238
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:27,720
You like me.

239
00:14:28,510 --> 00:14:29,240
Give it to me!

240
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:29,720
What's wrong?

241
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:30,290
How shameless.

242
00:14:30,290 --> 00:14:31,150
Shame on you.

243
00:14:31,510 --> 00:14:32,750
Let go of me! Go away!

244
00:14:33,890 --> 00:14:35,130
You said you like me.

245
00:14:36,080 --> 00:14:36,960
Let go of me!

246
00:14:36,980 --> 00:14:38,150
So shameless.

247
00:14:42,550 --> 00:14:43,000
What?

248
00:14:43,510 --> 00:14:44,960
So many people are watching.

249
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:46,220
And you won't admit it?

250
00:14:46,630 --> 00:14:47,870
You said you like me!

251
00:14:47,930 --> 00:14:50,130
You asked me out to meet you by the river!

252
00:14:52,890 --> 00:14:54,620
Wang Jianhua? Someone like him

253
00:14:54,910 --> 00:14:56,790
would throw himself at me

254
00:14:57,050 --> 00:14:58,910
without me even lifting a finger.

255
00:15:00,150 --> 00:15:00,840
Xia Ziyu,

256
00:15:01,480 --> 00:15:03,630
maybe you should take a good look
in the mirror

257
00:15:03,630 --> 00:15:04,550
and see

258
00:15:04,790 --> 00:15:06,190
how incompetent you are.

259
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:13,660
Darn northern girl,

260
00:15:13,690 --> 00:15:15,020
cheating me of my money!

261
00:15:18,670 --> 00:15:19,670
Do you want to die?

262
00:15:33,870 --> 00:15:34,960
Xia Xiaolan.

263
00:15:36,580 --> 00:15:37,980
Why can't I get rid of you?

264
00:15:39,550 --> 00:15:41,550
Why are you always going against me?

265
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:44,670
All my pain comes from you.

266
00:15:45,990 --> 00:15:47,700
Everyone else can live well,

267
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:50,160
but not you.

268
00:15:52,640 --> 00:15:53,200
Lady!

269
00:15:53,220 --> 00:15:54,680
Do you have an invitation?

270
00:15:54,800 --> 00:15:56,920
You can't enter without an invitation.

271
00:15:56,920 --> 00:15:58,160
Are you blind?

272
00:15:58,840 --> 00:15:59,760
I'm Ms. Vivi

273
00:15:59,790 --> 00:16:01,050
from Chengrong Group.

274
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:02,610
Do I even need an invitation

275
00:16:02,750 --> 00:16:04,350
to get into a place like this?

276
00:16:04,550 --> 00:16:05,510
Friends from the media,

277
00:16:05,510 --> 00:16:06,710
you may come forward.

278
00:16:31,550 --> 00:16:32,100
What's happening?

279
00:16:32,100 --> 00:16:33,030
She's bleeding.

280
00:16:35,390 --> 00:16:37,740
Should we call an ambulance for her?

281
00:16:38,370 --> 00:16:40,230
Mr. Du, please come here quickly!

282
00:16:40,550 --> 00:16:41,430
I don't know.

283
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:44,490
Call an ambulance for me.

284
00:16:44,490 --> 00:16:45,730
Please call an ambulance for me.

285
00:16:45,730 --> 00:16:47,590
Someone call an ambulance for me.

286
00:17:28,190 --> 00:17:29,310
Is m-my child

287
00:17:29,330 --> 00:17:30,440
gone?

288
00:17:33,110 --> 00:17:34,040
It's in the past.

289
00:17:34,330 --> 00:17:35,860
Focus on recovering first.

290
00:17:38,240 --> 00:17:38,680
No.

291
00:17:39,360 --> 00:17:40,750
This was not an accident.

292
00:17:40,750 --> 00:17:43,350
It was Xia Xiaolan. It was Xia Xiaolan.

293
00:17:44,830 --> 00:17:45,510
Listen,

294
00:17:45,550 --> 00:17:47,150
don't let your mind run wild.

295
00:17:47,200 --> 00:17:49,240
Just focus on getting better now.

296
00:17:53,590 --> 00:17:54,400
Rest well.

297
00:18:05,260 --> 00:18:07,390
The Young Master has a message for you.

298
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:09,700
It's actually good that the child is gone.

299
00:18:09,700 --> 00:18:11,060
You can use a clean identity

300
00:18:11,060 --> 00:18:12,580
to carry out his plan.

301
00:18:13,080 --> 00:18:14,990
The choice is yours to make.

302
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:21,640
Tell the Young Master

303
00:18:21,960 --> 00:18:23,490
that I accept his proposal.

304
00:18:23,960 --> 00:18:25,360
I'll do whatever he says.

305
00:18:25,840 --> 00:18:26,270
Good.

306
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:28,600
I'll go back and tell him.

307
00:18:31,960 --> 00:18:32,720
Xia Xiaolan,

308
00:18:33,440 --> 00:18:35,110
I will climb up the social ladder.

309
00:18:35,110 --> 00:18:36,910
I will obtain wealth and status.

310
00:18:37,510 --> 00:18:38,710
When that time comes,

311
00:18:39,070 --> 00:18:40,200
I will make you taste

312
00:18:40,260 --> 00:18:42,190
what it's like to lose everything.

313
00:19:09,880 --> 00:19:11,030
Master.

314
00:19:17,830 --> 00:19:19,160
What are you doing here?

315
00:19:19,160 --> 00:19:20,420
Is this how you usually

316
00:19:20,500 --> 00:19:21,830
win the Old Man's favor?

317
00:19:25,760 --> 00:19:27,170
He really has gotten old.

318
00:19:28,520 --> 00:19:29,810
Such cheap tricks,

319
00:19:30,250 --> 00:19:31,710
and he still fell for them.

320
00:19:33,200 --> 00:19:34,930
But they don't work now, right?

321
00:19:35,550 --> 00:19:36,310
He probably

322
00:19:37,070 --> 00:19:38,670
won't come to meet you again.

323
00:19:40,550 --> 00:19:42,150
Isn't that all thanks to you?

324
00:19:42,640 --> 00:19:43,240
What?

325
00:19:44,920 --> 00:19:46,780
Are you dissatisfied with me now?

326
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:49,290
The Old Man doesn't come to me anymore,

327
00:19:49,750 --> 00:19:51,150
so you think I'm useless?

328
00:19:53,680 --> 00:19:55,540
Let me correct a mistake of yours.

329
00:19:56,440 --> 00:19:58,970
I've thought you were useless
for a long time.

330
00:19:59,350 --> 00:20:00,790
But if you were capable

331
00:20:00,900 --> 00:20:02,560
of winning the Old Man's favor

332
00:20:02,790 --> 00:20:03,760
and securing a place

333
00:20:03,760 --> 00:20:04,890
in our Du family,

334
00:20:05,440 --> 00:20:07,770
I wouldn't stand in the way
of your riches.

335
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:11,110
But what a pity.

336
00:20:13,110 --> 00:20:14,440
You were too impatient.

337
00:20:15,310 --> 00:20:16,910
You wasted the bright future

338
00:20:17,030 --> 00:20:17,920
you once had.

339
00:20:21,750 --> 00:20:22,680
What do you mean?

340
00:20:23,860 --> 00:20:24,590
You had already won

341
00:20:24,590 --> 00:20:25,680
the Old Man's favor

342
00:20:26,310 --> 00:20:28,170
and were pregnant with his child.

343
00:20:28,550 --> 00:20:29,220
If you'd just prepared well

344
00:20:29,220 --> 00:20:30,270
to be a mistress in the Du family,

345
00:20:30,270 --> 00:20:31,720
wouldn't that have been enough?

346
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:34,970
But you insisted on going
and picking a fight with Xia Xiaolan.

347
00:20:34,970 --> 00:20:36,110
If you hadn't tried to do that,

348
00:20:36,110 --> 00:20:36,720
maybe

349
00:20:38,160 --> 00:20:38,790
the Old Man

350
00:20:39,640 --> 00:20:41,700
would have rewarded you with a house.

351
00:20:46,680 --> 00:20:47,640
Du Zhaohui,

352
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:51,570
you're still obsessed
with Xia Xiaolan, aren't you?

353
00:20:53,240 --> 00:20:54,170
What do you mean?

354
00:20:55,150 --> 00:20:56,640
You want to help clear Xia Xiaolan
of suspicion,

355
00:20:56,640 --> 00:20:57,110
right?

356
00:20:57,840 --> 00:20:58,680
You want to convince me

357
00:20:58,680 --> 00:20:59,900
that losing the baby in my belly

358
00:20:59,900 --> 00:21:01,240
had nothing to do with her,

359
00:21:01,240 --> 00:21:03,440
and that it was just an accident, right?

360
00:21:03,960 --> 00:21:05,620
Do you think I'd believe that?

361
00:21:06,510 --> 00:21:07,440
Out of nowhere,

362
00:21:08,030 --> 00:21:09,370
she just happened to show up
on the same day as me,

363
00:21:09,370 --> 00:21:10,930
at the same hotel,

364
00:21:10,960 --> 00:21:11,960
on the same floor?

365
00:21:15,830 --> 00:21:16,550
Xia Ziyu,

366
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:18,590
don't go nuts.

367
00:21:20,550 --> 00:21:21,950
Sometimes I really doubt

368
00:21:22,070 --> 00:21:22,850
if you and Xia Xiaolan

369
00:21:22,850 --> 00:21:24,330
really grew up together

370
00:21:24,830 --> 00:21:25,490
as cousins.

371
00:21:27,200 --> 00:21:27,860
Xia Xiaolan

372
00:21:28,400 --> 00:21:28,960
doesn't even

373
00:21:28,960 --> 00:21:30,130
care about you at all.

374
00:21:30,130 --> 00:21:31,060
She would never,

375
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:32,590
nor does she need

376
00:21:32,590 --> 00:21:33,790
to use such despicable means

377
00:21:33,790 --> 00:21:34,720
to deal with you.

378
00:21:37,820 --> 00:21:39,000
You make it sound like she's

379
00:21:39,000 --> 00:21:40,730
some sort of innocent goddess.

380
00:21:41,680 --> 00:21:43,010
What makes her so noble?

381
00:21:43,940 --> 00:21:44,870
Doesn't she also

382
00:21:44,880 --> 00:21:45,830
rely on men?

383
00:21:49,000 --> 00:21:49,790
It's just

384
00:21:50,750 --> 00:21:53,280
that she doesn't rely on you,
Young Master Du.

385
00:21:55,180 --> 00:21:57,380
No matter how hard you try to please her,

386
00:21:58,720 --> 00:22:01,510
she still won't spare you a glance.

387
00:22:07,300 --> 00:22:08,270
I'm not sure if she'll

388
00:22:08,270 --> 00:22:09,270
spare me a glance.

389
00:22:10,030 --> 00:22:10,960
But I'm sure

390
00:22:11,720 --> 00:22:12,510
the Old Man

391
00:22:14,000 --> 00:22:15,800
won't spare you a single glance.

392
00:22:47,550 --> 00:22:48,480
This court finds

393
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:50,200
the defendants, Liu Tianquan,

394
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:52,920
Xiao Jianyong, Zhang Donglai,
and Zhang Sanjun,

395
00:22:52,920 --> 00:22:55,240
guilty of intentional homicide
and smuggling.

396
00:22:55,240 --> 00:22:57,510
In accordance with the laws
of the People's Republic of China,

397
00:22:57,510 --> 00:22:58,970
the verdict is as follows.

398
00:22:59,640 --> 00:23:01,110
Defendant Liu Tianquan

399
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:03,200
committed the crime
of intentional homicide

400
00:23:03,200 --> 00:23:04,750
by cruel means,

401
00:23:05,110 --> 00:23:06,600
causing extremely serious consequences,

402
00:23:06,600 --> 00:23:07,800
posing

403
00:23:07,830 --> 00:23:09,030
great threats to society.

404
00:23:09,030 --> 00:23:10,960
He is hereby sentenced to death

405
00:23:11,110 --> 00:23:12,750
and deprived of political rights for life

406
00:23:12,750 --> 00:23:13,750
as a punishment.

407
00:23:14,960 --> 00:23:16,360
Defendant Liu Tianquan,

408
00:23:16,590 --> 00:23:18,110
in his smuggling activities,

409
00:23:18,110 --> 00:23:20,310
violated national customs regulations.

410
00:23:20,310 --> 00:23:21,510
The circumstances are serious,

411
00:23:21,510 --> 00:23:22,750
causing major losses

412
00:23:22,770 --> 00:23:24,630
to national economic interests.

413
00:23:24,750 --> 00:23:26,590
In accordance with relevant laws,

414
00:23:26,590 --> 00:23:28,640
he is sentenced to 15 years in prison

415
00:23:29,110 --> 00:23:30,030
and fined

416
00:23:30,270 --> 00:23:32,150
5.5 million RMB

417
00:23:32,510 --> 00:23:34,770
to demonstrate the authority of the law.

418
00:23:34,850 --> 00:23:37,780
[Shengcheng People's Court]

419
00:23:36,270 --> 00:23:38,070
Xia Ziyu has fallen out of favor?

420
00:23:38,370 --> 00:23:39,370
The Old Man

421
00:23:39,400 --> 00:23:41,070
got tired of her a long time ago.

422
00:23:41,070 --> 00:23:43,330
He did it
for the sake of the child before.

423
00:23:43,440 --> 00:23:45,100
But now that the child is gone,

424
00:23:45,810 --> 00:23:46,640
the Old Man hasn't

425
00:23:46,640 --> 00:23:48,300
gone to see her for a long time.

426
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:49,880
However,

427
00:23:50,160 --> 00:23:51,590
because of what happened to Liu Tianquan,

428
00:23:51,590 --> 00:23:52,240
he seems to be treating

429
00:23:52,240 --> 00:23:54,110
Liu Keying a bit better recently.

430
00:23:55,680 --> 00:23:56,940
I really didn't expect

431
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:58,030
that the Old Man

432
00:23:58,520 --> 00:23:59,480
would actually hand over

433
00:23:59,480 --> 00:24:00,280
Liu Tianquan.

434
00:24:00,730 --> 00:24:02,220
To clean up its image, Chengrong Group

435
00:24:02,220 --> 00:24:03,090
severed a limb.

436
00:24:03,550 --> 00:24:05,030
The Du family has officially

437
00:24:05,030 --> 00:24:06,510
cut ties with shady businesses

438
00:24:06,510 --> 00:24:08,310
and turned to legal operations.

439
00:24:08,790 --> 00:24:09,450
Du Zhaohui,

440
00:24:09,790 --> 00:24:11,190
you chose the right path.

441
00:24:11,450 --> 00:24:12,440
It's a pity the Old Man is

442
00:24:12,440 --> 00:24:13,960
not completely heartless.

443
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:15,720
He only handed over Liu Tianquan.

444
00:24:15,720 --> 00:24:16,520
You know what?

445
00:24:16,560 --> 00:24:17,410
The smuggling ring was

446
00:24:17,410 --> 00:24:18,080
in the hands

447
00:24:18,110 --> 00:24:19,240
of Brat Ji all along.

448
00:24:19,400 --> 00:24:20,110
Two days ago,

449
00:24:20,110 --> 00:24:21,640
he warned Brat Ji

450
00:24:22,200 --> 00:24:24,310
to cut off all the smuggling businesses.

451
00:24:24,310 --> 00:24:25,510
Usually, that guy

452
00:24:25,840 --> 00:24:27,590
dresses up like some decent gentleman.

453
00:24:27,590 --> 00:24:28,350
I didn't expect

454
00:24:28,350 --> 00:24:30,160
that he'd want to be a gangster
more than I do.

455
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:31,320
His reaction seemed

456
00:24:31,350 --> 00:24:32,030
even more nervous

457
00:24:32,030 --> 00:24:32,830
than when he lost

458
00:24:32,830 --> 00:24:34,030
that 5% of the shares.

459
00:24:36,580 --> 00:24:37,230
Listen,

460
00:24:37,790 --> 00:24:39,190
you'd better be careful.

461
00:24:39,270 --> 00:24:40,240
Xia Ziyu

462
00:24:40,510 --> 00:24:41,680
hates your guts.

463
00:24:42,310 --> 00:24:43,400
Thanks for the heads-up.

464
00:24:43,400 --> 00:24:44,600
I'll take it to heart.

465
00:24:44,970 --> 00:24:45,800
I think

466
00:24:45,830 --> 00:24:47,690
you should also watch out for Du Zhaoji.

467
00:24:47,690 --> 00:24:48,560
He's just

468
00:24:48,590 --> 00:24:50,320
as small-minded as Xia Ziyu is.

469
00:24:50,510 --> 00:24:51,310
You're so smug now.

470
00:24:51,310 --> 00:24:53,440
Be careful, he might plot against you.

471
00:24:54,120 --> 00:24:54,830
Is there anything else?

472
00:24:54,830 --> 00:24:56,090
If not, I'm hanging up.

473
00:24:56,240 --> 00:24:56,700
Hold on.

474
00:24:58,350 --> 00:24:59,750
Are you worried about me?

475
00:25:00,960 --> 00:25:01,640
So,

476
00:25:01,890 --> 00:25:02,960
you've forgiven me for hiding things

477
00:25:02,960 --> 00:25:03,590
from you?

478
00:25:04,440 --> 00:25:06,590
I haven't been to Shengcheng
for a long time.

479
00:25:06,590 --> 00:25:08,590
How about we grab a coffee tomorrow?

480
00:25:08,790 --> 00:25:09,590
No.

481
00:25:09,960 --> 00:25:11,890
Zhou Cheng and I are going back
to Anqing tomorrow.

482
00:25:11,890 --> 00:25:13,350
We'll handle the scholarship first,

483
00:25:13,350 --> 00:25:14,830
then return to Jingcheng
for our marriage certificate.

484
00:25:14,830 --> 00:25:16,200
As for coffee, let's talk about it

485
00:25:16,200 --> 00:25:16,800
next time.

486
00:25:19,320 --> 00:25:25,240
♪ Why do you always say that line? ♪

487
00:25:25,260 --> 00:25:30,890
♪ Why am I unwilling to give up? ♪

488
00:25:30,160 --> 00:25:31,790
Call the department store manager over
for me.

489
00:25:30,910 --> 00:25:37,140
♪ I realize that love
shouldn't mean losing it all ♪

490
00:25:32,510 --> 00:25:34,310
I want to pick

491
00:25:34,830 --> 00:25:36,290
a wedding gift for Ms. Xia.

492
00:25:36,570 --> 00:25:37,510
No problem, Young Master.

493
00:25:37,430 --> 00:25:42,540
♪ Yet somehow, I can't help but like you ♪

494
00:25:37,830 --> 00:25:38,890
I'll go get him now.

495
00:25:44,510 --> 00:25:45,240
How did it go?

496
00:25:46,110 --> 00:25:47,160
The verdict is out.

497
00:25:47,160 --> 00:25:48,160
We won the lawsuit

498
00:25:48,350 --> 00:25:50,550
and got the appropriate compensation.

499
00:25:50,790 --> 00:25:52,350
Mr. Wu, Mr. Zhou,

500
00:25:52,830 --> 00:25:53,510
thank you.

501
00:25:53,950 --> 00:25:55,480
Thanks to you not giving up,

502
00:25:55,560 --> 00:25:56,440
we finally got justice

503
00:25:56,440 --> 00:25:57,540
for Shi Kai.

504
00:25:58,350 --> 00:25:58,940
Thank you both.

505
00:25:58,940 --> 00:26:00,740
It's nothing. Don't mention it.

506
00:26:03,640 --> 00:26:04,170
Alright,

507
00:26:04,400 --> 00:26:05,240
you guys go ahead.

508
00:26:05,240 --> 00:26:06,880
I'll send Ms. Wei back to the hotel.

509
00:26:06,880 --> 00:26:08,210
When are you going back?

510
00:26:08,680 --> 00:26:09,280
Tomorrow.

511
00:26:09,830 --> 00:26:10,590
We'll stay for a couple of days

512
00:26:10,590 --> 00:26:11,640
and then come back.

513
00:26:11,640 --> 00:26:12,840
It won't affect work.

514
00:26:13,070 --> 00:26:13,530
Come on.

515
00:26:13,750 --> 00:26:14,510
It's rare for you to go back.

516
00:26:14,510 --> 00:26:15,920
Why not stay a few more days?

517
00:26:15,920 --> 00:26:17,980
Consider it my gift to your marriage.

518
00:26:18,110 --> 00:26:18,710
We're off.

519
00:26:21,000 --> 00:26:21,930
Thank you.

520
00:26:24,440 --> 00:26:25,440
Drive carefully.

521
00:26:26,720 --> 00:26:27,650
We'll get going.

522
00:26:32,200 --> 00:26:33,000
Drive safely.

523
00:26:34,400 --> 00:26:34,930
Let's go.

524
00:26:49,240 --> 00:26:51,170
Congratulations, Attorney Zhou.

525
00:26:52,640 --> 00:26:53,270
Thank you,

526
00:26:53,880 --> 00:26:54,510
Mrs. Zhou.

527
00:27:18,350 --> 00:27:19,410
What are you doing?

528
00:27:20,550 --> 00:27:21,800
-Mr. Tang.
-Mr. Tang.

529
00:27:22,780 --> 00:27:23,550
You're already here.

530
00:27:23,550 --> 00:27:24,350
Hurry inside.

531
00:27:25,550 --> 00:27:25,960
Okay.

532
00:27:35,880 --> 00:27:37,140
Take the fruit basket.

533
00:27:41,590 --> 00:27:42,190
After you.

534
00:27:45,510 --> 00:27:46,040
Mrs. Liu.

535
00:27:46,160 --> 00:27:47,890
-Mom.
-You came back together?

536
00:27:48,480 --> 00:27:49,240
I happened

537
00:27:49,270 --> 00:27:50,640
to run into them at the door.

538
00:27:50,640 --> 00:27:50,960
Mom,

539
00:27:50,990 --> 00:27:53,050
Zhou Cheng bought some soda and wine.

540
00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:55,600
You put the soda on the table?

541
00:27:55,790 --> 00:27:57,320
It needs to go to the fridge.

542
00:27:57,480 --> 00:27:58,740
Show some initiative.

543
00:27:59,270 --> 00:27:59,640
Okay.

544
00:28:00,400 --> 00:28:00,920
Well,

545
00:28:01,310 --> 00:28:01,750
Tang,

546
00:28:02,130 --> 00:28:03,350
go to the kitchen and help me check

547
00:28:03,350 --> 00:28:04,510
the heat of my soup.

548
00:28:04,860 --> 00:28:05,960
I still can't master the cooking

549
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:07,070
of this Cantonese soup.

550
00:28:07,070 --> 00:28:08,550
I'm afraid it won't taste good.

551
00:28:08,550 --> 00:28:10,210
Any soup you make tastes good.

552
00:28:11,120 --> 00:28:12,380
So you didn't buy wine?

553
00:28:13,530 --> 00:28:14,400
Why are you still standing there?

554
00:28:14,400 --> 00:28:15,640
Hurry into the kitchen.

555
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:16,070
Okay.

556
00:28:16,270 --> 00:28:16,870
I'm going.

557
00:28:17,050 --> 00:28:17,640
Go ahead.

558
00:28:22,030 --> 00:28:23,830
What's going on with those two?

559
00:28:24,590 --> 00:28:26,650
Nothing.

560
00:28:26,680 --> 00:28:28,000
We just stayed in the car for a while

561
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:28,530
just now.

562
00:28:29,160 --> 00:28:30,400
What were you and Zhou Cheng

563
00:28:30,400 --> 00:28:31,330
doing in the car?

564
00:28:33,790 --> 00:28:34,590
Just...

565
00:28:46,720 --> 00:28:47,720
Gently.

566
00:28:48,420 --> 00:28:48,830
Okay.

567
00:28:49,920 --> 00:28:50,680
Harder.

568
00:28:51,590 --> 00:28:52,590
Keep kneading it.

569
00:28:53,430 --> 00:28:55,360
Didn't you master it well just now?

570
00:29:07,000 --> 00:29:07,730
Why so rough?

571
00:29:08,920 --> 00:29:10,120
I failed to go gently.

572
00:29:10,440 --> 00:29:11,700
You're still so young.

573
00:29:12,830 --> 00:29:14,890
Sometimes you can't control it well.

574
00:29:17,240 --> 00:29:17,770
Xiaolan.

575
00:29:18,200 --> 00:29:19,150
Zhou is not bad.

576
00:29:19,170 --> 00:29:20,960
He is learning to knead dough
with Mr. Tang.

577
00:29:20,960 --> 00:29:21,960
He knows the right force,

578
00:29:21,960 --> 00:29:23,030
handling it with ease.

579
00:29:23,030 --> 00:29:23,790
Really?

580
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:25,000
He's that gifted?

581
00:29:25,920 --> 00:29:27,480
I could smell Fen's soup

582
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:29,160
from miles away.

583
00:29:29,360 --> 00:29:30,450
We're all late.

584
00:29:30,480 --> 00:29:31,310
Sorry for that. Sorry.

585
00:29:31,310 --> 00:29:32,400
You bought so many things.

586
00:29:32,400 --> 00:29:32,960
This is great.

587
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:34,310
Hello, Auntie, Xiaolan.

588
00:29:34,310 --> 00:29:35,570
Hello. Hello, Taotao.

589
00:29:35,790 --> 00:29:37,560
If it smells good, eat more tonight.

590
00:29:37,560 --> 00:29:38,480
Mr. Tang and Zhou Cheng are teaching

591
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:41,610
and learning how to knead dough
in the kitchen upstairs.

592
00:29:41,790 --> 00:29:43,160
He's working in the kitchen?

593
00:29:43,160 --> 00:29:43,600
Right.

594
00:29:44,590 --> 00:29:45,030
Good.

595
00:29:46,000 --> 00:29:47,720
He just needs to learn

596
00:29:47,780 --> 00:29:49,310
the kitchen work properly.

597
00:29:49,480 --> 00:29:50,540
I'll go take a look.

598
00:29:51,020 --> 00:29:52,420
What kind of talk is that?

599
00:29:52,830 --> 00:29:53,490
Ignore him.

600
00:29:54,240 --> 00:29:55,200
I've got your back.

601
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:55,600
Right?

602
00:29:55,790 --> 00:29:56,850
We all support you.

603
00:29:57,240 --> 00:29:59,360
What's going on today?

604
00:29:59,430 --> 00:30:00,510
Why are Uncle and Mr. Tang

605
00:30:00,510 --> 00:30:01,750
so fond of Zhou Cheng?

606
00:30:02,240 --> 00:30:03,480
What's going on here?

607
00:30:03,830 --> 00:30:05,350
What else could it be?

608
00:30:05,720 --> 00:30:08,250
A father-in-law nitpicking his son-in-law.

609
00:30:08,870 --> 00:30:09,480
Granny Yu.

610
00:30:09,510 --> 00:30:11,030
Quickly, say hello to Granny Yu.

611
00:30:11,030 --> 00:30:12,030
Hello, Granny Yu.

612
00:30:12,160 --> 00:30:12,790
Hello.

613
00:30:19,200 --> 00:30:19,790
Cheng,

614
00:30:20,070 --> 00:30:22,130
did you make the dough for these buns?

615
00:30:22,720 --> 00:30:23,070
Yes.

616
00:30:23,920 --> 00:30:25,580
I learned from Mr. Tang today.

617
00:30:26,400 --> 00:30:26,930
The buns.

618
00:30:28,000 --> 00:30:29,590
You'll get
your marriage certificate tomorrow.

619
00:30:29,590 --> 00:30:30,830
Why are you in such a rush?

620
00:30:30,830 --> 00:30:32,430
Can't the wedding wait a bit?

621
00:30:34,070 --> 00:30:35,070
Of course I'm in a rush.

622
00:30:35,070 --> 00:30:36,210
If I don't hurry,

623
00:30:36,340 --> 00:30:37,800
what if Xiaolan runs away?

624
00:30:38,880 --> 00:30:39,960
As outstanding as she is,

625
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:41,510
I'm not the only one who likes her.

626
00:30:41,510 --> 00:30:42,970
Others will like her, too.

627
00:30:43,680 --> 00:30:44,740
But marriage isn't

628
00:30:44,960 --> 00:30:46,310
about tying her down.

629
00:30:46,920 --> 00:30:47,590
She

630
00:30:48,030 --> 00:30:48,790
and her heart

631
00:30:49,350 --> 00:30:50,410
will still be free.

632
00:30:51,550 --> 00:30:52,960
If I don't do well,

633
00:30:53,510 --> 00:30:54,920
she can still leave me.

634
00:30:55,830 --> 00:30:56,400
But I won't

635
00:30:56,400 --> 00:30:57,480
let that happen.

636
00:30:58,000 --> 00:30:59,460
Although life in the future

637
00:30:59,460 --> 00:31:00,920
may not be smooth sailing,

638
00:31:01,200 --> 00:31:02,730
because we love each other,

639
00:31:02,940 --> 00:31:04,470
we're willing to join hands

640
00:31:04,480 --> 00:31:06,140
to enter the next stage of life

641
00:31:06,480 --> 00:31:07,480
and to face together

642
00:31:07,480 --> 00:31:08,790
various challenges

643
00:31:08,920 --> 00:31:10,120
the future may bring.

644
00:31:11,790 --> 00:31:13,280
Well said!

645
00:31:13,310 --> 00:31:15,240
Let's give him a round of applause!

646
00:31:16,070 --> 00:31:16,550
Dad,

647
00:31:17,200 --> 00:31:17,790
Mr. Tang,

648
00:31:18,160 --> 00:31:19,210
are you satisfied

649
00:31:19,240 --> 00:31:20,640
with Zhou Cheng's reply?

650
00:31:21,640 --> 00:31:22,820
What do you mean by "satisfied"...

651
00:31:22,820 --> 00:31:23,950
You little traitor!

652
00:31:24,070 --> 00:31:24,830
Come on.

653
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:25,360
Cheers.

654
00:31:25,360 --> 00:31:26,000
Cheers.

655
00:31:26,070 --> 00:31:27,130
Congratulations.

656
00:31:34,510 --> 00:31:35,850
Looking back now,

657
00:31:35,880 --> 00:31:36,640
it feels like

658
00:31:37,030 --> 00:31:38,510
it was a lifetime ago.

659
00:31:40,590 --> 00:31:42,110
Back then,

660
00:31:43,720 --> 00:31:45,780
you didn't care much about anything.

661
00:31:46,070 --> 00:31:47,480
But during that time,

662
00:31:48,510 --> 00:31:50,310
you were always so cautious

663
00:31:50,960 --> 00:31:51,830
and wary.

664
00:31:52,640 --> 00:31:54,040
Every day, it seemed like

665
00:31:54,960 --> 00:31:56,830
you were looking for something.

666
00:31:58,790 --> 00:31:59,590
So,

667
00:32:00,510 --> 00:32:02,480
you noticed it, too.

668
00:32:04,910 --> 00:32:06,150
I gave birth to you.

669
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:08,160
I'm your mom.

670
00:32:09,200 --> 00:32:10,600
How could I not notice it?

671
00:32:16,200 --> 00:32:17,240
But I thought

672
00:32:18,200 --> 00:32:19,270
my daughter

673
00:32:19,830 --> 00:32:21,560
had suffered so much injustice

674
00:32:22,310 --> 00:32:23,640
and been through a lot.

675
00:32:24,750 --> 00:32:26,210
No matter what she became,

676
00:32:27,510 --> 00:32:29,110
she'd always be my daughter.

677
00:32:31,550 --> 00:32:33,160
As long as we're together,

678
00:32:34,240 --> 00:32:35,500
nothing else matters.

679
00:32:42,960 --> 00:32:44,290
What's wrong, Xiaolan?

680
00:32:46,240 --> 00:32:46,830
Nothing.

681
00:32:49,270 --> 00:32:49,720
Mom,

682
00:32:50,550 --> 00:32:51,240
I love you.

683
00:32:54,920 --> 00:32:56,030
I love you too.

684
00:33:07,830 --> 00:33:09,640
I don't know if it's possible

685
00:33:10,270 --> 00:33:11,510
that Liu Fen realized

686
00:33:12,200 --> 00:33:13,000
I'm not his daughter

687
00:33:13,000 --> 00:33:14,330
by spotting the change.

688
00:33:15,880 --> 00:33:17,070
But no matter what,

689
00:33:17,510 --> 00:33:19,000
she gave me selfless,

690
00:33:19,160 --> 00:33:20,160
complete love,

691
00:33:20,960 --> 00:33:22,620
allowing the past Xia Xiaolan

692
00:33:22,800 --> 00:33:24,610
to become a braver Xia Xiaolan.

693
00:33:26,310 --> 00:33:27,920
She gave so much love

694
00:33:28,870 --> 00:33:30,870
and also received so much in return.

695
00:33:41,380 --> 00:33:43,000
[Anqing No. 1 High School]
[A warm welcome to alumna Xia Xiaolan]

696
00:33:44,270 --> 00:33:46,270
A warm welcome to Xia Xiaolan?

697
00:33:47,160 --> 00:33:48,160
Xia Xiaolan?

698
00:33:49,360 --> 00:33:49,970
Why does

699
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:51,550
this name sound so familiar?

700
00:33:51,550 --> 00:33:52,280
Here you are.

701
00:33:52,400 --> 00:33:53,330
What does she do?

702
00:33:54,000 --> 00:33:55,920
You don't know Xia Xiaolan?

703
00:33:56,310 --> 00:33:57,510
She was Yunan Province's top scorer

704
00:33:57,510 --> 00:33:59,510
in the college entrance exam back then.

705
00:33:59,510 --> 00:34:01,430
She's a big boss now.

706
00:34:01,590 --> 00:34:03,270
She even won an architectural award.

707
00:34:03,270 --> 00:34:04,530
She's really amazing.

708
00:34:04,640 --> 00:34:06,350
My business was just average back then,

709
00:34:06,350 --> 00:34:07,550
but she gave me some advice,

710
00:34:07,550 --> 00:34:08,670
and suddenly,

711
00:34:08,800 --> 00:34:09,710
it took off.

712
00:34:10,710 --> 00:34:12,280
She's been smart since she was a kid.

713
00:34:12,280 --> 00:34:12,880
Last time,

714
00:34:13,070 --> 00:34:14,000
she donated

715
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:16,110
a library to the school.

716
00:34:17,030 --> 00:34:18,560
This time, she's setting up

717
00:34:19,590 --> 00:34:20,449
a scholarship!

718
00:34:20,880 --> 00:34:22,400
In the future, local kids

719
00:34:22,659 --> 00:34:24,280
who can't afford school fees

720
00:34:24,320 --> 00:34:25,670
will have solutions!

721
00:34:29,550 --> 00:34:30,409
President Sun,

722
00:34:30,920 --> 00:34:31,850
look who's here.

723
00:34:36,480 --> 00:34:37,480
Xiaolan?

724
00:34:38,440 --> 00:34:39,449
Mr. Sun.

725
00:34:39,780 --> 00:34:41,190
Hello, hello.

726
00:34:41,360 --> 00:34:42,150
Long time no see.

727
00:34:42,150 --> 00:34:42,840
Indeed.

728
00:34:44,480 --> 00:34:45,440
You've changed.

729
00:34:45,960 --> 00:34:47,070
You've matured

730
00:34:47,440 --> 00:34:48,710
and become more beautiful.

731
00:34:48,710 --> 00:34:49,600
And you.

732
00:34:49,630 --> 00:34:50,400
You haven't changed a bit.

733
00:34:50,400 --> 00:34:51,480
You're still so young.

734
00:34:51,480 --> 00:34:52,550
Not at all.

735
00:34:52,710 --> 00:34:53,110
Look

736
00:34:53,280 --> 00:34:55,110
at all my gray hair.

737
00:34:55,320 --> 00:34:56,650
I'm retiring next year.

738
00:34:56,920 --> 00:34:59,000
I didn't expect I could see you back here

739
00:34:59,000 --> 00:35:00,860
to visit me before my retirement.

740
00:35:01,280 --> 00:35:02,440
I get it.

741
00:35:02,480 --> 00:35:03,520
Mr. Sun, you're blaming me

742
00:35:03,520 --> 00:35:04,670
for not coming back to visit you often.

743
00:35:04,670 --> 00:35:05,710
No, not at all.

744
00:35:07,450 --> 00:35:08,160
Who is this?

745
00:35:08,190 --> 00:35:09,280
This is Zhou Cheng.

746
00:35:10,030 --> 00:35:11,190
My fiancé.

747
00:35:11,760 --> 00:35:12,560
Hello, hello.

748
00:35:12,590 --> 00:35:13,520
Nice to meet you.

749
00:35:14,110 --> 00:35:15,440
What a decent young man!

750
00:35:15,770 --> 00:35:16,370
Thank you.

751
00:35:16,550 --> 00:35:17,710
Let me show you

752
00:35:18,000 --> 00:35:18,510
around the school

753
00:35:18,510 --> 00:35:19,360
to see all the changes.

754
00:35:19,360 --> 00:35:20,190
I'll give you a tour.

755
00:35:20,190 --> 00:35:20,590
Let's go.

756
00:35:20,590 --> 00:35:20,920
Okay.

757
00:35:21,550 --> 00:35:22,080
Xiaolan,

758
00:35:22,360 --> 00:35:24,070
our school has changed a lot.

759
00:35:24,360 --> 00:35:25,440
The old desks

760
00:35:25,720 --> 00:35:27,920
and chairs have all been replaced.

761
00:35:27,280 --> 00:35:30,150
[Reminisce about the youth and talk
about the lasting ties with the alma mater]

762
00:35:34,280 --> 00:35:35,190
Students,

763
00:35:35,920 --> 00:35:37,590
today, our alumna,

764
00:35:37,710 --> 00:35:39,070
Miss Xia Xiaolan,

765
00:35:39,150 --> 00:35:41,360
came back to establish a scholarship.

766
00:35:41,710 --> 00:35:42,440
I

767
00:35:42,890 --> 00:35:44,070
insisted on having her

768
00:35:44,070 --> 00:35:45,110
talk to you all.

769
00:35:46,110 --> 00:35:47,920
Over the years, Xiaolan

770
00:35:48,230 --> 00:35:50,550
has risen from a rural background

771
00:35:50,880 --> 00:35:52,320
through her own efforts,

772
00:35:52,550 --> 00:35:54,760
starting at our Anqing No.1 High School,

773
00:35:54,760 --> 00:35:55,960
moving on to Huaqing,

774
00:35:56,110 --> 00:35:57,240
then to Shengcheng,

775
00:35:57,450 --> 00:35:58,920
and finally to the front lines

776
00:35:58,920 --> 00:36:00,000
of socialist construction.

777
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:01,720
And after achieving success,

778
00:36:01,960 --> 00:36:03,960
she hasn't forgotten
to give back to her alma mater.

779
00:36:03,960 --> 00:36:05,230
Her life experience

780
00:36:05,360 --> 00:36:06,600
will surely

781
00:36:06,630 --> 00:36:07,670
inspire you all.

782
00:36:08,360 --> 00:36:10,360
Let's give a round of applause

783
00:36:10,480 --> 00:36:12,800
to welcome Miss Xia Xiaolan.

784
00:36:23,440 --> 00:36:24,070
Students,

785
00:36:24,320 --> 00:36:25,000
hello.

786
00:36:25,360 --> 00:36:26,320
I am Xia Xiaolan.

787
00:36:27,670 --> 00:36:29,070
I used to be just like you,

788
00:36:29,670 --> 00:36:31,440
longing to find in a few words,

789
00:36:31,840 --> 00:36:33,070
in a good book,

790
00:36:33,440 --> 00:36:34,730
or in a speech,

791
00:36:35,000 --> 00:36:36,480
the secret to success.

792
00:36:37,080 --> 00:36:38,000
As if once I grasped

793
00:36:38,000 --> 00:36:38,880
this secret,

794
00:36:39,210 --> 00:36:40,290
I could find

795
00:36:40,320 --> 00:36:41,670
a shortcut to success.

796
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:43,630
But sorry,

797
00:36:44,110 --> 00:36:44,800
I'm going

798
00:36:44,900 --> 00:36:46,300
to disappoint you today.

799
00:36:47,150 --> 00:36:48,150
Because I am still

800
00:36:48,150 --> 00:36:49,550
on the path of searching.

801
00:36:52,030 --> 00:36:53,670
Some of you might think

802
00:36:54,440 --> 00:36:56,840
I seem to have succeeded already.

803
00:36:57,300 --> 00:36:58,280
Am I just unwilling

804
00:36:58,280 --> 00:36:59,410
to share it with you?

805
00:37:00,840 --> 00:37:02,190
That is not the case.

806
00:37:02,930 --> 00:37:04,120
I have indeed made

807
00:37:04,150 --> 00:37:05,560
some brilliant achievements

808
00:37:05,560 --> 00:37:06,590
and gained something

809
00:37:06,590 --> 00:37:08,000
I once desired.

810
00:37:08,710 --> 00:37:10,510
But during this process,

811
00:37:10,760 --> 00:37:12,440
that wasn't the goal.

812
00:37:13,510 --> 00:37:14,710
My goal was

813
00:37:14,800 --> 00:37:16,070
to seek an answer.

814
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:18,550
What kind of person do I

815
00:37:18,550 --> 00:37:19,810
really want to become,

816
00:37:20,800 --> 00:37:22,860
and what kind of life do I want to live?

817
00:37:24,070 --> 00:37:25,400
Studying in a small place

818
00:37:25,400 --> 00:37:26,840
like Anqing,

819
00:37:27,320 --> 00:37:28,590
many students are

820
00:37:28,800 --> 00:37:30,760
from underdeveloped rural areas.

821
00:37:31,760 --> 00:37:32,800
Perhaps you think

822
00:37:33,150 --> 00:37:34,760
that from birth,

823
00:37:35,190 --> 00:37:37,450
we are already many steps behind others.

824
00:37:38,030 --> 00:37:39,560
Then isn't pursuing dreams

825
00:37:40,070 --> 00:37:41,590
and life ideals

826
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:43,510
just a pipe dream?

827
00:37:43,820 --> 00:37:45,300
Cheap and good!

828
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:47,550
But I don't think so.

829
00:37:48,760 --> 00:37:50,940
Despite the different starting points,

830
00:37:50,940 --> 00:37:52,900
the roads to a dream life are all

831
00:37:53,100 --> 00:37:54,760
filled with twists and turns.

832
00:37:54,960 --> 00:37:56,550
Finding the answer to life is

833
00:37:56,550 --> 00:37:57,880
just like doing a test.

834
00:37:59,150 --> 00:38:00,030
Sometimes,

835
00:38:00,540 --> 00:38:02,130
you can't immediately choose

836
00:38:02,130 --> 00:38:03,990
the right answer with certainty.

837
00:38:04,260 --> 00:38:05,360
Instead, you need to eliminate

838
00:38:05,360 --> 00:38:06,550
many wrong options.

839
00:38:08,360 --> 00:38:09,440
Back in Anqing,

840
00:38:09,920 --> 00:38:11,650
I didn't have any grand ideals.

841
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:13,030
I only wanted to escape

842
00:38:13,030 --> 00:38:14,630
this hard life.

843
00:38:15,550 --> 00:38:18,840
So, ever since
the National College Entrance Examination,

844
00:38:18,840 --> 00:38:19,840
I've done everything

845
00:38:19,840 --> 00:38:21,070
in my power

846
00:38:21,480 --> 00:38:23,410
to get rid of the life I didn't want.

847
00:38:25,590 --> 00:38:26,800
To find

848
00:38:27,020 --> 00:38:28,550
the final correct answer is

849
00:38:28,550 --> 00:38:29,280
really hard.

850
00:38:30,280 --> 00:38:32,710
Sometimes, you'll face difficulties.

851
00:38:33,360 --> 00:38:35,760
Sometimes, you'll encounter setbacks.

852
00:38:36,880 --> 00:38:38,340
Not just bumps in the road,

853
00:38:39,030 --> 00:38:40,190
but true suffering.

854
00:38:42,070 --> 00:38:44,800
But as long as you grit your teeth
and keep pushing

855
00:38:44,920 --> 00:38:46,320
just a little bit longer,

856
00:38:47,030 --> 00:38:48,960
these things won't matter anymore.

857
00:38:48,960 --> 00:38:50,710
You will surely gain more.

858
00:38:52,120 --> 00:38:52,850
You will find

859
00:38:52,880 --> 00:38:54,680
friends sharing the same goals,

860
00:38:54,800 --> 00:38:56,190
a more determined self,

861
00:38:56,670 --> 00:38:58,880
and a clearer direction in life.

862
00:38:59,720 --> 00:39:00,410
I hope you

863
00:39:00,440 --> 00:39:02,100
won't be afraid of the future.

864
00:39:02,150 --> 00:39:03,670
Don't let fear

865
00:39:04,030 --> 00:39:05,490
make you lose your dreams.

866
00:39:05,840 --> 00:39:07,350
Social conventions

867
00:39:07,630 --> 00:39:08,760
won't limit you.

868
00:39:09,440 --> 00:39:11,370
The only thing that can limit you is

869
00:39:11,440 --> 00:39:12,550
yourselves.

870
00:39:13,920 --> 00:39:14,630
Success is

871
00:39:15,200 --> 00:39:16,680
a prize found

872
00:39:16,710 --> 00:39:18,570
on the journey to life's answers.

873
00:39:19,000 --> 00:39:20,930
What's more important than that is

874
00:39:21,010 --> 00:39:21,880
